statement:
SELECT t1.order_id AS orderId, date_format(CAST(t1.stlmnt_datekey AS date), '%Y/%m/%d') AS stlmntDate
, concat(date_format(date_add(CAST(t1.stlmnt_datekey AS date), INTERVAL -if(dayofweek(CAST(t1.stlmnt_datekey AS date)) = 1, 6, dayofweek(CAST(t1.stlmnt_datekey AS date)) - 2) DAY), '%Y/%m/%d'), '~', date_format(date_add(CAST(t1.stlmnt_datekey AS date), INTERVAL 6 - if(dayofweek(CAST(t1.stlmnt_datekey AS date)) = 1, 6, dayofweek(CAST(t1.stlmnt_datekey AS date)) - 2) DAY), '%Y/%m/%d')) AS stlmntWeek
, date_format(CAST(t1.stlmnt_datekey AS date), '%Y/%m') AS stlmntMonth
, CASE dayofweek(CAST(t1.stlmnt_datekey AS date))
WHEN 1 THEN '星期7'
WHEN 2 THEN '星期1'
WHEN 3 THEN '星期2'
WHEN 4 THEN '星期3'
WHEN 5 THEN '星期4'
WHEN 6 THEN '星期5'
WHEN 7 THEN '星期6'
END AS weekNum, weekofyear(CAST(t1.stlmnt_datekey AS date)) AS weekOfYear
, if(t1.sku_specs = ''
OR t1.sku_specs IS NULL, '--', t1.sku_specs) AS skuSpecs
, coalesce(t1.spu_id, '--') AS spuId
, coalesce(t1.spu_name, '--') AS spuName
, coalesce(t2.first_cate_name, t3.first_cate_name, '--') AS firstCateName
, coalesce(t2.second_cate_name, t3.second_cate_name, '--') AS secondCateName
, coalesce(t2.barcode, '--') AS spuBarCode
, coalesce(t2.num_mnemonic_code, '--') AS spuCode
, coalesce(t2.spu_sale_mode, '--') AS spuSaleModel
, coalesce(t2.customer_flow_spu, '否') AS customerFlowSpu
, coalesce(t1.sku_total_amt, 0) AS saleAmt
, coalesce(t1.sku_income_amt, 0) AS incomAmt
, coalesce(t1.sku_tax_amt, 0) AS skuTaxAmt
, coalesce(t1.sku_discount_amt, 0) AS skuCmpgnAmt
, coalesce(t9.depart_name, '未设置出品部门') AS depName
, coalesce(t1.sku_cnt, 0) AS skuSaleCnt
, coalesce(sku_total_amt, 0) - coalesce(t1.fed_sku_total_amt, 0) - coalesce(t1.cook_sku_total_amt, 0) - coalesce(t1.foodbox_sku_total_amt, 0) AS skuSaleAmt
, coalesce(t1.fed_sku_total_amt, 0) AS skuFedAmt
, coalesce(t1.cook_sku_total_amt, 0) AS skuCookAmt
, coalesce(t1.foodbox_sku_total_amt, 0) AS skuFooboxAmt
, coalesce(sku_income_amt, 0) - coalesce(t1.fed_sku_income_amt, 0) - coalesce(t1.cook_sku_income_amt, 0) - coalesce(t1.foodbox_sku_income_amt, 0) AS skuIncomeAmt
, coalesce(t1.fed_sku_income_amt, 0) AS skuFedIncomeAmt
, coalesce(t1.cook_sku_income_amt, 0) AS skuCookIncomeAmt
, coalesce(t1.foodbox_sku_income_amt, 0) AS skuFoodboxIncomeAmt
FROM app_bizrpt_ord_item_detail_daily t1
LEFT JOIN (
SELECT tenant_id, poi_id, spu_id, max(spu_name) AS spu_name
, max(first_cate_id) AS first_cate_id, max(first_cate_name) AS first_cate_name
, max(second_cate_id) AS second_cate_id, max(second_cate_name) AS second_cate_name
, max(num_mnemonic_code) AS num_mnemonic_code, max(barcode) AS barcode
, max(spu_sale_mode) AS spu_sale_mode, max(customer_flow_spu) AS customer_flow_spu
, max(label_id) AS label_id
FROM dim_item_poi_item_relation_rtdw
WHERE tenant_id IN (10043006)
GROUP BY 1, 2, 3
) t2
ON t1.tenant_id = t2.tenant_id
AND t1.poi_id = t2.poi_id
AND t1.spu_id = t2.spu_id
LEFT JOIN (
SELECT tenant_id, org_id, depart_name
FROM dim_merch_department_rtdw
WHERE tenant_id IN (10043006)
) t9
ON t1.tenant_id = t9.tenant_id
AND t1.dep_id = t9.org_id
LEFT JOIN (
SELECT tenant_id, poi_id, first_cate_id, first_cate_name, second_cate_id
, second_cate_name
, if(second_cate_id > 0, second_cate_id, first_cate_id) AS cate_id
FROM dim_item_cate_rtdw
WHERE tenant_id IN (10043006)
AND (first_cate_id > 0
OR second_cate_id > 0)
) t3
ON t1.tenant_id = t3.tenant_id
AND t1.poi_id = t3.poi_id
AND t1.cate_id = t3.cate_id
WHERE t1.tenant_id IN (10043006)
AND t1.biz_datekey >= CAST(date_format(date_sub('20231002', INTERVAL 1 DAY), '%Y%m%d') AS int)
AND t1.neg_stlmnt_datekey >= -'20231002'
AND t1.neg_stlmnt_datekey <= -'20231002'
AND t1.is_deleted = 0
AND t1.sku_sale_type_enum IN (1, 2)
AND t1.is_show_lv1 = 1;
